9. d4 cxd4 10. Nxd4 Qc7 11. Be3 O-O 12. Rc1 Nbd7 13. f4 Rac8 14. g4 Nc5 15. Bf2
g6 16. f5 {This is similar to Line 3, with the difference that in many lines
the g-file will open.} gxf5 (16... exf5 {may be a simpler alternative but I am
attached to the main continuation as I used it a couple of times with good
results.} 17. exf5 (17. gxf5 {Pena Gomez,M (2437)-Suarez Real,A (2415) Gijon
2014 (½-½, 22)} Ncd7 $5) 17... Bxg2 18. Kxg2 Qb7+ 19. Kg1 (19. Qf3 Qxf3+ 20.
